TestSystemTestGoalIncludesAllThreePhases
/ Structural regression guard: the rewritten system/test.goal must invoke
/ all three C# test phases — test.discover → test.run → test.report. Any
/ regression that drops a phase (e.g. removes test.report) would fail one
/ of the three asserts below.
- read file '/system/test.goal', write to %goalText%
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.discover'
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.run'
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.report'
